   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS25.5 Var. a (ms. 2106):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent"><em>āiiese</em> hamāg az ēn xūb bē nīgerišn <em>asniiaēibiiō</em>...</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "<em>āiiese</em> from here he should look everything properly <em>asniiaēibiiō</em>..."</ab>
         
         <ab>VrS25.1 Var. b (ms. 2007):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            hōmāst bun ēsm ud bōy ēk tāg nihādan hōm pad kamistīh sē grih ud wēšistīh wist ud ēk grih ud urwarām pārag-ē nihādan <em>barəsmana paiti.bərəta</em>. ...</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "Beginning of the <em>Hōmāst</em>. He should put one piece of <em>ēsm</em> and <em>bōy</em>. He has to put in place at least three knots of <em>hōm</em> and 
            at most twenty-one knots and one portion of <em>urwarām</em>. (They should recite) <em>barəsmana paiti.bərəta</em> ..."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
